name: Agent
line: Uh oh, I think the helicopter is broken.

name: Agent
line: Come on, come on. Come on.

name: Rick
line: Come get this delicious brine. Come get this brine, motherfucker! Come on! Come get that delicious brittle. Come here, motherfuckers!! Come on, mother fuckers! Come here! Come home to the delicious brittleness of tiny insects and delicious flavor!

name: Agent
line: Come home to tiny, delicious ides, tiny insects, tiny tiny seeds. Come home now, tiny seeds, please.

name: Agent
line: It's okay, Beth. We're taking fire from an automated turret. It's the only way to destroy an unregistered gun.

name: Rick
line: Morty, do you still love me?

name: Rick
line: Don't think about it! You'll end up fine as an insect or snake or something for a fraction of the people who think you are scary.

name: Agent
line: Mm. Ohh, my God! Oh! Oh, my god! Ohhhh!
